## 📞 Support & Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

**"ModuleNotFoundError"**
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

**"Port already in use"**
Edit app.py last line:
```python
app.run(debug=True, port=5001)
```

**"File not parsing"**
- Ensure it's a valid PDF/DOCX
- Check file size < 10MB
- Try a different file

**"Skills not detected"**
- Check if skill is in skills_master.json
- Try exact skill name
- Check resume contains the skill text

